<i>adjective</i>: 서글프다 [서글프다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>서글프다 [서글프다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. plaintive; forlorn; sorrowful</dd><br>
<dd>슬프고 외롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>Sad and lonely.</dd><br>
<dd>2. displeased; upset</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 들지 않고 섭섭하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Dissatisfied and disappointed.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>